    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not just a \"struggle\" though. people treat it like a phase you get over, but i've looked at everything and there is literally nothing there. no god, no destiny, just physics and entropy. there's no way to make it meaningful if it's just a biological accident. it's just exhausting to keep pretending it matters.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
